<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q28_v3" title="Q28_v3" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Registro de cambio de moneda aproximado:<br />- Moneda A: reales brasileños (R$)<br />- Moneda B: euros (€)<br />- Tipo de cambio: 7 R$ corresponden a 1,3 €<br />- Dinero disponible: 210 R$</p>
    <p>¿Aproximadamente cuántos euros recibirá al cambiar 210 R$?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">30 €<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Como <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mn>7</mn><mo>R$</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>1,3</mn><mo>€</mo></mrow></math>, entonces <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mn>210</mn><mo>R$</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>210</mn><mn>7</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>1,3</mn><mo>€</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>30</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>1,3</mn><mo>€</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>39</mn><mo>€</mo></mrow></math>. Por lo tanto, 30 € no corresponde al cambio de 210 R$.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">39 €<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Como <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mn>7</mn><mo>R$</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>1,3</mn><mo>€</mo></mrow></math> y <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mn>210</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>30</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>7</mn></mrow></math>, se reciben <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mn>30</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>1,3</mn><mo>€</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>39</mn><mo>€</mo></mrow></math>. Aproximadamente recibirá 39 €.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">390 €<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El cálculo correcto es <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mn>210</mn><mo>R$</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>210</mn><mn>7</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>1,3</mn><mo>€</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>30</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>1,3</mn><mo>€</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>39</mn><mo>€</mo></mrow></math>. Por lo tanto, 390 € es 10 veces mayor que el valor obtenido y no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">1130 €<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Usando el tipo de cambio dado, <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mn>210</mn><mo>R$</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>210</mn><mn>7</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>1,3</mn><mo>€</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>30</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>1,3</mn><mo>€</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>39</mn><mo>€</mo></mrow></math>. Entonces 1130 € no corresponde al cambio aproximado de 210 R$.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la equivalencia de cambio</strong></p>
            <p>El enunciado dice que 7 R$ corresponden a 1,3 €.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Ver cuántos grupos de 7 R$ hay en 210 R$</strong></p>
            <p>
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mrow>
                  <mn>210</mn><mo>÷</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>30</mn>
                </mrow>
              </math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces, 210 R$ equivalen a 30 grupos de 7 R$.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Convertir esos 30 grupos a euros</strong></p>
            <p>Si cada grupo de 7 R$ vale 1,3 €, entonces:</p>
            <p>
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mrow>
                  <mn>30</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>1,3</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>39</mn>
                </mrow>
              </math>
            </p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, al cambiar 210 R$ se reciben aproximadamente 39 €.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa que coincide con el resultado obtenido es 39 €.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La respuesta correcta es la alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>